                  "body": {
                    "type": "TextualBody",
                    "value": "<p rend=\"align(right)\"><date>May 26 1857</date>.</p>\n            <p>Revd Dear Sir</p>\n            <p rend=\"indent(3)\">I would feel obliged by your sending<lb/> for the use of the School,\n                Two quires of good letter paper,<lb/> and a package of envelopes, (self sealing).\n                    <persName>Mr Noot</persName> has<lb/> used fully one-half the supply sent last\n                time.</p>\n            <p rend=\"indent(1)\">He says he will take more care<lb/> of his portion for the\n                future.</p>\n            <p rend=\"indent(9)\">I am Revd Dr Sir</p>\n            <p rend=\"indent(9)\">yrs. Respectfully.</p>\n            <p rend=\"indent(10)\">\n                <persName role=\"author\">C. Smyth</persName>\n            </p>\n            <p><addressee>Revd I. Leeser</addressee>.</p>\n            <p rend=\"indent(1)\">School Director</p>\n            <pb n=\"Envelope\"/>\n            <p>\n                <addressee>Revd. I. Leeser</addressee>\n            </p>\n            <p rend=\"indent(1)\">\n                <placeName>Philadelphia</placeName>\n            </p>\n            <p rend=\"indent(2)\">\n                <placeName>Pen</placeName>\n            </p>\n        </body>\n    </text>\n</TEI>"
                  },
                  "target": "https://colenda.library.upenn.edu/items/ark:/81431/p3rf5m18z/canvas/p1"
                }
              ]
            }
